description: Try our easy to follow Chia Banana & Date Muffins recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Chia Banana & Date Muffins Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Divide mixture among muffin holes and top each with banana slices. Bake for 20 minutes or until a skewer inserted into the centre comes out clean. Serve warm or at room temperature.
